categories: Category:Commerce and labor guilds and unions

nodes.text: The Guild of Armament Distributors was a Wroonian guild. It was declared illegal by Governor Norrin and its guild hall was raided by Imperial forces. Kabalard Vinne, a representative of the Guild before it was dissolved, later led a retaliation strike on the Victory-class Star Destroyer Rampant in the Wroona Stardock.
